學員到災區做「治療」及藉此募捐。<br />\n不過，協會對外發放的訊息，以及杜永政宣稱的「白宮認可專家」資格，卻引起權威臨床心理學家的質疑。聯合國屬下組織更向本刊證實，已去信該會嚴正要求不要跟其扯上關係。"},{"pid":"51a0641da86959f26249cf5c88a759533f4de93b","tid":1281311,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"e5c0011b8e29d8564e15b9968d58d6ba75e37c55","tid":1281311,"uid":269643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c55e4f9e741b48658e0995d9582bda2494748c9","tid":1281311,"uid":43067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47e09ef94866e686e9b80dee355b18beb535a65","tid":1281311,"uid":269643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"見有post 話佢親建制，會出賣求協助者資料。親建制與否我唔清楚，但我上過其創辦人杜永政嘅workshop, 覺得佢嘅誠信有問題，好識manipulate 人，大家情緒受困擾嘅都唔好去搵呢間輔導中心。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"佢點manipulate 人法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"佢會講部分嘢（而呢d 嘢通常係上得workshop 嘅人最想知嘅)俾人聽，引起人注意或好奇心，之後叫人再嚟之後嘅workshop, 話會對個題目嘅認識或輔導技巧有幫助。真係去到時發現佢只係為自己嘅輔導課程向一d現職clinical psychologists 賣廣告, 佢應該怕人數唔夠多要多d人嚟做勢。另一樣嘢我無證實（因為我並非參加者）係佢帶隊出field 做災後輔導，有參加者質疑過盤數唔tally. <br />\n<br />\n其實香港有其他提供counseling 嘅團體，希望大家情緒有困擾投助reliable 嘅機構啦。"},{"pid":"272a38b845d24eca81add9df88d55fb313a8e49f","tid":1281311,"uid":269643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"今日壹週刊報道: <br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_679790_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_679790_0&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVz2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=5df4a21c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_679790_0&h=e5f59665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_679790_0</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2T1Q6j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2T1Q6j.png&h=b8059f8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"731d23b1488c753